{% extends 'help/base.modal.twig' %} 

{% block helpcontent %}
<p>This "summary" is made up of the sentences that openEssayist thinks are the most prominent 
and noticeable sentences in your assignment.</p>

<p>These are the sentences that openEssayist thinks sum up best what your assignment is about. </p>

<p>Using the "Sort by" control, you can change the order of sentences in the "summary":</p>

<ul>
<li> Use <button class="btn btn-small disabled">Importance</button> to show the most important sentences first, as detected by the system. 
<li> Use <button class="btn btn-small disabled">Text Order</button> to show the sentences in the order they appear in your text.

</ul> 
{% endblock %}

{% block hintcontent %}
<ul class="icons-ul">
  <li><i class="icon-li icon-comments"></i>Do you agree with openEssayist that these sentences are a good summary of your assignment?</li>
  <li><i class="icon-li icon-comments"></i>Are any important ideas that you want to convey missing from this summary? </li>
  <li><i class="icon-li icon-comments"></i>Are there lots of sentences in the summary that are about something that you think is unimportant or irrelevant to your assignment? </li>
  
</ul>

{% endblock %}
